Big Bank & DJ Scream welcome The West Coast Legend Daz Dillinger. The discussion includes The Cannabis Industry, Tupac, Snoop Dogg, Nate Dogg, Street Politics and more! Six The Goddis also joins the BIG FACTS crew to discuss Gender Roles, Masculinity, Feminism, Infidelity and more!
